TITLE: Last Known Good

Dedication:
A gift honoring family legacy, continuity, stewardship, and the preservation of knowledge.

Presented as:
Last Known Good

Purpose:
To record a stable reference point before future change, providing a snapshot of values, lessons learned, and continuity for future generations.

Principles:
- Preserve what works.
- Document what matters.
- Protect institutional memory.
- Leave clear handoffs.
- Measure progress against known-good states.

Statement:
Every generation inherits both opportunity and responsibility. A last known good state is not an ending; it is a trusted foundation from which future work can begin.

Classification:
.suit Reference Document
Status: Last Known Good
Framework: iV7
